description.narrative: Income Oxfam Novib HIVOS Fund management and Linking <(>&<)> Learning for Voice.

participating-org.narrative: Started in April 2016, Voice is a new consortium between Hivos and Oxfam Novib contracted and financed by the Netherlands Ministry of Foreign Affairs. The key objective of Voice is to empower the most marginalised and discriminated groups by strengthening the influencing capacity of civil society organisations and their representatives. Voice will do this by providing various types of grantsthrough open calls at global and country level, encouraging innovation as well as a linking and learning component. Empower, amplify and influence are the key principles of Voice.
